						</p>
						<ul>
							<li>
								Who is the user?
							</li>
							<li>
								What problem does this solve?
							</li>
							<li>
								What should the result look like?
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					
				</div>
				<div class="card" style="border-radius: 0 10px 0 0;">
					<p class="section-title" style="color: #3bff9a">
