							</li>
							<li>
								Become familiar with the structure.
							</li>
							<li>
								Figure out where the new additions will fit best.
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="card" style="border-radius: 0 0 0 10px;">
					<p class="section-title" style="color: #ff51f6">
