							</li>
							<li>
								What are the advantages and disadvantages of each approach?
							</li>
							<li>
								Given the system, which solution is most appropriate?
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="card" style="border-radius: 0 0 10px 0;">
					<p class="section-title" style="color: #ffe23b">
